# PlooM Installation guide

## Requirements
- A kubernetes cluster with a `GatewayClass`
- A minimal ArgoCD installed in its own namespace
  
This *Bootstrap* ArgoCD can be installed with the command line :
```bash
kubectl create namespace argocd
kubectl apply -n argocd --server-side --force-conflicts -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj/argo-cd/stable/manifests/install.yaml
```